snippet.title: Alice in Borderland – Saison 3 | Bande-annonce officielle VF | Netflix France
snippet.description:
La série ALICE IN BORDERLAND est désormais le titre japonais de Netflix le plus regardé dans le monde.

Les redoutables "jeux" qui ont bouleversé le monde entier sont de retour.

Dans la saison précédente, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) et Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) ont terminé toutes les parties et sont revenus dans le monde réel. Ils se sont mariés depuis et mènent ensemble une vie heureuse. Leurs souvenirs du monde parallèle ont été effacés, mais ils en voient des aperçus fugaces dans leurs rêves et leurs hallucinations. Un jour, Usagi disparaît soudainement, entraînée par un chercheur spécialisé dans l'au-delà prénommé Ryuji (#KentoKaku). Au moment de la disparition d'Usagi, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) remet à Arisu la dernière carte : le joker.

Le voyage inconnu, mené par la mystérieuse carte joker, est sur le point de se dévoiler…

ALICE IN BORDERLAND saison 3, disponible dans le monde entier le 25 septembre 2025, seulement sur Netflix.

#AliceinBorderlandS3, #AliceinBorderland3, #Netflix.

snippet.title: 🔴 EN DIRECT LANCEMENT STARSHIP SPACEX IFT-10 (Dixième vol Starship S37 SuperHeavy B16)
snippet.description:
Lancement du Starship S37 de SpaceX ! Cette mission tentera le premier déploiement de satellite dans l'espace et le premier retour d'un Starship V2 après l'explosion de tous les modèles V2 précédents ! 
* Acheter le patch de mission Starship Flight Test 10 ► https://www.ufotinik.com/produit/patch-starship-flight-10/

Pour tous savoir sur l'ambitieux programme de SpaceX pour son vaisseau spatial Starship ► https://youtu.be/N82JH8aHeKw
Pour ne louper aucun lancement abonne toi à ma chaîne ► http://bit.ly/1OuvrcM (merci ! )

Envie de soutenir la chaîne ? 
* Don direct ► https://www.paypal.com/paypalme/ufotinik
* Devenir sponsor afin de débloquer des avantages exclusifs sur la chaine (Icône, smiley , couleur spéciale de ton nom dans le tchat en direct....) ► https://cutt.ly/7hu7OSq
* Acheter le patch de mission Starship Flight Test 10 ► https://www.ufotinik.com/produit/patch-starship-flight-10/

Venez discuter avec les autres abonnés sur le discord  ► https://discord.gg/36z2xFm

Mes réseaux sociaux:
► Instagram : https://instagram.com/ufotinik
► Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/ufotinik
► Twitter : https://twitter.com/ufotinik

Horaires: Fenêtre de tir  01h30 - 02h30 UTC+2 (heure de Paris)
Base de lancement : Rampe de lancement orbitale A, Starbase, Texas, États-Unis
Destination: Orbite terrestre basse
Les prochains lancements ► https://www.ufotinik.com/calendrier-des-lancements-spatiaux/

Starship est une fusée dont l’objectif est d’amener l’Homme sur Mars. Elle est développée par la société d’Elon Musk: SpaceX. 
Starship est composé de deux étages. Le premier étage appelé SuperHeavy et le second étage Starship. Ce lanceur orbital super lourd a une particularité très forte car il sera entièrement réutilisable ! Cela veut dire que, non seulement le premier étage Super Heavy sera récupéré, et c’est une technologie qu’on peut voir avec la Falcon 9 de SpaceX, mais également que le deuxième étage Starship sera récupéré. Starship possède plusieurs configurations. C’est un système de transport de charge lourde (comme des satellites ou du carburants) mais aussi une capsule pour aller sur la station spatiale, un atterrisseur lunaire et un atterrisseur martien ! C’est quand même dingue ! Ah et j'oubliais, SpaceX prévoit également d’utiliser un Starship pour faire un saut en haute atmosphère pour rendre accessible n’importe quel point de la Terre en 30 minutes.

Ce dixième test en vol se concentrera sur trois objectifs principaux : 
- Quatrième lancement d'un Starship V2 suite aux échecs des vols précédents et l'explosion de S36 sur le pas de tir de test.
- Premier déploiement dans l'espace ! SpaceX déploiera des simulateurs Starlink qui reviendront dans l'océan Pacifique.
- Tests de nouveaux systèmes de bouclier thermique. 

STARSHIP :
Hauteur : 123 m 
Diamètre : 9 m 
Masse: 5370 tonnes 
Etages : 2
Propulsion premier étage Superheavy : 20 Raptor Boost + 13 Raptor Center
Propulsion deuxième étage Starship : 3 Raptor Center + 3 Raptor Vacuum
Ergols: LCH4 (méthane) et LOX (Oxygène Liquide)

snippet.title: Return to Silent Hill - Official Teaser Trailer (2025) Jeremy Irvine, Hannah Emily Anderson
snippet.description:
Christophe Gans, who directed 2006's Silent Hill, is back behind the camera for Return to Silent Hill, a sequel slated to arrive in theaters in 2026. Jeremy Irvine and Hannah Emily Anderson star in the sequel, which based on Konami's Silent Hill 2.

Return to Silent Hill brings the iconic horror franchise back to the screen. When James receives a mysterious letter from his lost love Mary, he is drawn to Silent Hill—a once-familiar town now consumed by darkness. As he searches for her, James faces monstrous creatures and unravels a terrifying truth that will push him to the edge of his sanity.

snippet.title: The Savant — Official Trailer | Apple TV+
snippet.description:
By day, Jodi is your average suburban mom. By night, she’s uncovering the darkest corners of the internet. Jessica Chastain is The Savant premiering September 26 on Apple TV+
https://apple.co/_TheSavant

The Savant is starring and executive produced by Academy, SAG, Golden Globe and Critics Choice Award-winner Jessica Chastain (“The Eyes of Tammy Faye,” “The Good Nurse,” “George & Tammy,” Broadway’s “A Doll’s House”). The eight episode thriller will make its global debut on Apple TV+ with the first two episodes on Friday, September 26, 2025, followed by one new episode every Friday through November 7, 2025.

The tense and high-stakes thriller follows an undercover investigator known as The Savant as she infiltrates online hate groups in an effort to stop domestic extremists before they act. Alongside Chastain, The Savant also stars Nnamdi Asomugha, Cole Doman, Jordana Spiro, Trinity Lee Shirley, Toussaint Francois Battiste, and guest star Pablo Schreiber.

Hailing from FIFTH SEASON, The Savant is executive produced by Chastain and Kelly Carmichael for Freckle Films, Emmy Award winner Alan Poul (“Six Feet Under,” “Tokyo Vice”), Emmy Award nominee Melissa James Gibson (“Anatomy of a Scandal,” “House of Cards,” “The Americans”), and six-time Emmy Award winner and two-time DGA winner Matthew Heineman (“A Private War,” “Retrograde,” “Cartel Land”). David Levine and Garrett Kemble serve as executive producers for Anonymous Content. Andrea Stanley, writer of the original Cosmopolitan feature, serves as a consultant.

snippet.title: Lukas Graham - 7 Years (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Subscribe and press (🔔) to join the Notification Squad and stay updated with new uploads

Download Stream - http://smarturl.it/LukasGrahamAlbum

Follow Lukas Graham:
https://www.instagram.com/lukasgraham
https://www.facebook.com/LukasGraham
https://www.tiktok.com/@lukasgraham

Follow Gseven Records:
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/gsevenrecords/
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/gsevenrecords/

We have an official permission from the right holders to upload this music

Lyrics:

[Chorus]
Once, I was seven years old, my mama told me
Go make yourself some friends, or you'll be lonely
Once, I was seven years old

[Verse 1]
It was a big, big world, but we thought we were bigger
Pushing each other to the limits, we were learning quicker
By eleven, smoking herb and drinking burning liquor
Never rich, so we were out to make that steady figure

[Chorus]
Once, I was eleven years old, my daddy told me
Go get yourself a wife, or you'll be lonely
Once, I was eleven years old

[Verse 2]
I always had that dream like my daddy before me
So I started writing songs, I started writing stories
Something about that glory just always seemed to bore me
'Cause only those I really love will ever really know me

[Chorus]
Once, I was twenty years old, my story got told
Before the morning sun, when life was lonely
Once, I was twenty years old (Lukas Graham!)

[Verse 3]
I only see my goals, I don't believe in failure
'Cause I know the smallest voices, they can make it major
I got my boys with me, at least those in favor
And if we don't meet before I leave, I hope I'll see you later

[Chorus]
Once, I was twenty years old, my story got told
I was writing 'bout everything I saw before me
Once, I was twenty years old

[Bridge]
Soon, we'll be thirty years old, our songs have been sold
We've traveled around the world and we're still roaming
Soon, we'll be thirty years old

[Verse 4]
I'm still learning about life, 
my woman brought children for me
So I can sing them all my songs, and I can tell them stories
Most of my boys are with me, some are still out seeking glory
And some I had to leave behind, 
my brother, I'm still sorry

[Chorus]
Soon, I'll be sixty years old, my daddy got sixty-one
Remember life and then your life becomes a better one
I made a man so happy when I wrote a letter once
I hope my children come and visit once or twice a month
[Breakdown]
Soon, I'll be sixty years old, will I think the world is cold?
Or will I have a lot of children who can warm me?
Soon, I'll be sixty years old
Soon, I'll be sixty years old, will I think the world is cold?
Or will I have a lot of children who can hold me?
Soon, I'll be sixty years old

[Chorus]
Once, I was seven years old, my mama told me
"Go make yourself some friends, or you'll be lonely"
Once I was seven years old
Once I was seven years old

snippet.title: Honest Trailers | Jurassic World: Rebirth
snippet.description:
It’s the Honest Trailer for Jurassic World: Rebirth! This wasn’t so bad was it? Or have our standards just fallen that low? Either way this is the same ol’ dino chow they’ve been feeding us since the 90’s, only this time…there’s uh…more Altoids? The humans got better, the dinosaurs got worse, and we’ll all meet back here in two years to say more or less the same things about the next one.

If you’re still reading this, comment “ALAN!” below
